Here's the demonstration video which could explain my project:
  https://drive.google.com/file/d/1ijOiAAuK4qfmJQgu7U0ge8RvX8ALa6i6/view?usp=drivesdk

This is a cloud based web Application with which an user can buy product or add a product to cart for purchase it in future.
An admin can monitor the purchase of the user.also we can get recommendations of product with help of a chatbot.
User can get a confirmation mail for each of their login,registration and after purchasing a product.
